  "text": "Psychomotor testing was included in our protocol because it is thought to provide a more sensitive index of patient recovery compared to clinical assessment [CITATION_1] . It is assumed that test performance equates to an aptitude for real-life skills [CITATION_2] . Some interpretation is required to link our findings with potential clinical significance.",
